    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. Six factors are appropriately scoped out at MRL 2 per ASME V&V 40 Table 1. The CFD hemolysis model is accepted as credible for identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II centrifugal blood pump under CPB conditions. This model has been applied in clinical research to support device design decisions and regulatory submissions.",
